{
  "name": "Elemental Specialization",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Ninjutsu </p><p>You have begun to specialize in a particular element of your choice.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Select one Nature Release Keyword (Earth, Wind, Fire, Water, Lightning).</p><p> You may ignore Hand Seal (HS) requirement for Ninjutsu of C-Rank of lower with your chosen nature release.</p><p>• You deal additional damage with Ninjutsu with your chosen Nature Release Keyword, equal to its rank.</p><p> (D- Rank: 1, C-Rank: 2, B-Rank: 3, A-Rank: 4, S-Rank: 5) </p><p>• You reduce the chakra cost of Ninjutsu with your chosen Nature Release keyword by an amount equal to its rank.</p><p> (D-Rank: 1, C-Rank: 2, B-Rank: 3, A-Rank: 4, S-Rank: 5).</p><p>• You can take this feat multiple times, each time selecting a different element.</p><p></p>",
